high_descs: Go around the kitchen island to the counter space on the left of the stove.
Pick up the gray knife under the salt shaker on the counter..
Move closer to the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three parts.
Place the knife on the right of the salt shaker in front.
Pick up one piece of the apple form the counter.
Turn right to go to the sink.
Wash the apple under the running water and take it out.
Turn around and go to the trash can on the floor on the left of the stove.
Place the apple in to the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out the washed apple piece.

high_descs: Go to the counter left of the stove
Pick up a butterknife
Look at the apple on the counter
Cut the apple into pieces
Place the butterknife on the counter
Pick up an apple piece
Go to the sink
Wash the apple in the sink
Go to the bin
Place the apple piece in the bin
anns.task_desc: Place a cut and washed apple piece in a bin

high_descs: Head to the left of the oven
Grab the knife off of the counter
Look up at the counter
Cut the apple on the counter into three slices
Put the knife down on the counter
Grab one of the slices of apple
Turn right and go to the sink
Wash the apple in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and go to the trash can
Put the apple in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Putting a sliced apple in the trash can
